item.title: CVE-2022-23764|2024-08-03T03:51:46.048Z -- teruten%20co.%2Cltd -- webcube
item.description: The vulnerability causing from insufficient verification procedures for downloaded files during WebCube update. Remote attackers can bypass this verification logic to update both digitally signed and unauthorized files, enabling remote code execution.
